    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is ideal for someone looking for a dependable mode of transportation without the premium price tag of a newer model. The exterior shows some clear signs of age, including several noticeable scratches on the passenger side doors and some minor paint oxidation on the roof. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows typical wear and some light staining on the rear bench seat. Mechanically, it starts reliably and runs well, though it will eventually need attention for a minor oil seep and some suspension bushings that are nearing the end of their life. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that gets the job done.",
