    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a dream to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014I\u2019ve made sure to keep up with all the maintenance, so it runs like a champ. It\u2019s got a few tiny signs of love here and there, but it\u2019s super clean and ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for something reliable and fun, this is definitely the one for you! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
