      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for the discerning driver is this E92-generation M3, featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 with independent throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline. This example is equipped with a 6-speed longitudinal manual transmission and the M-Variable locking differential, providing exceptional mechanical grip and linear power delivery. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators to ensure the longevity of the high-strung valvetrain. The chassis remains sharp with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and a structurally sound subframe. While the exterior displays minor stone chips consistent with spirited use, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response remain peak-spec for this iconic M-division platform.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Clean title. Regular maintenance performed. Interior and exterior well-kept. Functional and reliable.",
      "price": 32500.0,
