    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle offers the perfect balance of performance and practicality. The exterior finish retains a deep luster, complemented by a clean, smoke-free interior featuring premium upholstery with only minor signs of character consistent with careful use. Mechanically, it stands in solid form with a smooth-shifting transmission, responsive handling, and a recently serviced engine that runs quiet and strong. All electronics function exactly as intended, from the premium sound system to the ice-cold dual-zone climate control. While you may find a few tiny stone chips from highway driving, the car has been primarily garage-kept and treated with respect. It is a turnkey example, recently inspected and ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver. Meticulously maintained and presenting in commendable condition, it offers a refined driving experience and proven mechanical integrity. Every aspect of this automobile reflects a consistent standard of care, ensuring it remains a sophisticated and reliable choice for its next owner. We invite you to experience this distinguished balance of performance and long-term value.",
      "price": 34800.0,
