      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me over the years. I've taken great care of it, so it still looks wonderful and drives even better! It's perfect for someone who wants a dependable car that\u2019s ready for any adventure. I'd love for it to go to a good home\u2014come by, say hi, and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 33500.0,
